<section id="additional_services" class="inner_sections">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large-5 columns copy">
			<h2>Additional services</h2>
			<p>H.Engage implementations are turnkey and we have plenty of easy to follow documentation. If you need some extra assistance, we have Client Experience Consultants to help. Please contact us and we can provide you with a quote based on your needs. Prices typically range $300 to $3000.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="large-6 columns services_include">
			<p class="caption">Services include:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><span>&raquo;</span><p>Prize structure</p></li>
				<li><span>&raquo;</span><p>Population engagement</p></li>
				<li><span>&raquo;</span><p>Content creation</p></li>
				<li><span>&raquo;</span><p>Game mechanics</p></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<section id="pricing_faq" class="inner_sections">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="large-6 columns">
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>Is all software included?</span></p>
				<p>Yes, all software is included. We don’t have any “modules” to upgrade. If we add a new feature, it’s included in the price you’ve already paid.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>Are there any extra costs I could incur?</span></p>
				<p>We provide up to 3 hours of support setting up your system in the first month. There are very few cases where that’s not enough. If you need more support, we can provide you with a quote.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>Does employee support cost extra?</span></p>
				<p>No it does not cost extra. Our Client Experience Consultants are here to assist your employees if they have any technical difficulties. Support is open 9 AM to 7 PM ET.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>Are there any discounts?</span></p>
				<p>Sign up for an annual subscription and get a discounted rate equivalent to three months free.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="large-6 columns">
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>What if I change my mind?</span></p>
				<p>If you want to discontinue your use of H.Engage for any reason within the first 30 days of signing-up, we will refund your money in full, no questions asked.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>What counts as a user?</span></p>
				<p>Anyone that is uploaded into the system as an eligible participant is counted as a user. So for example, if you invite ten people to use the system, you would be charged for ten users.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>Can I suspend my plan and keep my user data?</span></p>
				<p>If you decide to cancel your plan, we'll keep your data on file for 30 days before deleting it.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="pricing_question large-10">
				<p><span>More questions?</span></p>
				<a href="#!" class="request_a_demo pop-button">Contact us</a>
			</div>
		</div>
</section>

<script>
$('.chart_tabs li').click(function (){
	$('.chart_tabs li').removeClass("active");
	$(this).addClass("active");
});
$('#annual_plan').click(function () {
	$('#monthly_prices').hide();
	$('#annual_prices').show();
});
$('#monthly_plan').click(function () {
	$('#annual_prices').hide();
	$('#monthly_prices').show();
});
</script>

